<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Little Abrm Bakes</title>

<style>
body {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    font-family: "Berlin Sans FB", sans-serif;
    background-color: #FFF6ED;
    color: #4A2C2A;
}

/* Header */
header {
    background-color: #F4C2C2;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 20px;
}

header h1 {
    font-family: "Segoe Script", cursive;
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 42px;
}

/* Section box */
section {
    width: 85%;
    margin: 20px auto;
    padding: 20px;
    background-color: #FFFDF9;
    border-radius: 15px;
    box-shadow: 0px 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

/* Section titles */
.title {
    font-family: Forte, cursive;
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    color: #8B4513;
}

ul {
    margin-left: 20px;
}

/* Footer */
footer {
    background-color: #F4C2C2;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 15px;
    margin-top: 20px;
    font-family: "Segoe Script", cursive;
    font-weight: bold;
}

a {
    color: #8B4513;
    font-weight: bold;
    text-decoration: none;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
    <h1>Little Abrm Bakes</h1>
</header>

<section>
    <div class="title">About Us</div>
    <p>
        Little Abrm Bakes is a home-based bakery business that provides fresh and delicious mini baked items such as mini cakes, donuts, cupcakes, cookies, brownies and custom sweet treats. These treats are perfect for birthdays, small celebrations, gifts and personal cravings.
    </p>
</section>

<section>
    <div class="title">Products / Services</div>
    <ul>
        <li>Mini Cake</li>
        <li>Cupcakes</li>
        <li>Donuts</li>
        <li>Desserts</li>
        <li>Drinks</li>
        <li>Snacks</li>
    </ul>
</section>

<section>
    <div class="title">Mission</div>
    <p>
        Our mission is to provide fresh, homemade and high-quality baked treats that bring happiness in every bite.
    </p>
</section>

<section>
    <div class="title">Vision</div>
    <p>
        Our vision is to become a trusted and loved mini bakery brand known for delicious small treats and beautiful presentation.
    </p>
</section>

<section>
    <div class="title">Brand Value</div>
    <p>We believe:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Small things create big happiness</li>
        <li>Quality matters</li>
        <li>Homemade with love</li>
    </ul>
</section>

<section>
    <div class="title">Conclusion</div>
    <p>
        Little Abrm Bakes focuses on delivering fresh and high-quality mini desserts that bring joy and sweetness to everyday moments and small celebrations.
    </p>
</section>

